quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,43,"Mofte woo lajal majje ngal adotaako …óe, …ďe nee…ďnantake kadi."
  23,44,"Refti Min Nuli Nulaa…ďe amen …ďen ko …ďe jokkondir…ďe, tuma kala ari e mofte Nulaa…óo majje on …ďe njedda mo Min njokkini yoga e ma…ď…ďe yoga, Min mba…ói …ďe yewtereeji, wo…ó…óineede wonanii yim…ďe …ďe gooŇč…óintaa …ďen."
  23,45,"Refti Min Nuli Muusaa e musi…ó…óo makko on Haaruuna wond'ude e aayeeje amen …óen e hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  23,46,"Fa'ade e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'um ngun, …ďe mawnintinii …ďe laatii yim…ďe townitii…ďe."
  23,47,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Enee, hara min ngooŇč…óinat yim…ďe …ói…óo yeru amen, hara yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe ko maccu…ďe amen?""
  23,48,"∆Āe njeddi …ďen …ói…óo, …ďe laatii jiyaa…ďe e halkaa…ďe …ďen."
  23,49,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkiino Muusaa Deftere nde mbelejo'o kam…ďe …ďe peewa."
  23,50,"Min mba…ói ge…óal Mariyama on e neene makko Ma'ande, Min werni …ďe fa'ade e tulde joomiraare √Īi…ďrude e callungol."
  23,51,"Eey mon yo Nulaa…ďe, √Īaamee immorde e laa…ďu…ói …óin ngollon ko mo∆ī∆īi, pellet Min, Mi…óo Anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  23,52,"E pellet, kaa Diina mo'on ko Diina woota, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on lulee Kam."
  23,53,"∆Āe ta∆īi fiyaake ma…ď…ďe on hakkunde ma…ď…ďe dente, kala fedde no farnora ko woni kon ka mayre."
  23,54,"∆äalu …ďe e siwrere nde haa e dummunne."
  23,55,"Enee, hara …ďe cikku wonan'dema ko Min …ďeydiri …ďe kon immorde e jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe."
  23,56,"Min njaccinana …ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, ko woni …ďe tin'aa."
  23,57,"Pellet, …ďern …ďe ka√Īum immorde e kulol Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe hul…ďe."
  23,58,"E …ďen …ďe ka√Īum ko …ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe sayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  23,59,"E …ďeen …ďe ka√Īum …ďe nhonah sirkanoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe."